    		<section id="bio">
    			<p>William Carlos Williams defines a poem as "a small (or large) machine made out of words." More introductory BS.</p>.
    			<p>With Jonas, players tap words to create a story that can take unexpected directions. Simple drawing tools give players a chance to illustrate their journey.</p>
